---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Cookie Policy - JSON Formatter Pro"
  description="Learn about the cookies used by JSON Formatter Pro, how we use them, and how to manage your cookie preferences."
  path="/cookies"
  keywords="cookies, cookie policy, tracking, user preferences"
>
  <article class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-12 text-sm text-subtle">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-fg">Cookie Policy</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 text-xs text-subtle">Last updated: July 2026</p>

    <h2 class="mt-8 text-lg font-semibold text-fg">What Are Cookies?</h2>
    <p class="mt-2">
      Cookies are small text files that are stored on your device (computer, tablet, mobile phone) when you visit a website. They are widely used to make websites work more efficiently and provide useful information to website owners.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-8 text-lg font-semibold text-fg">Types of Cookies We Use</h2>

    <h3 class="mt-6 text-base font-semibold text-fg">1. Essential/Functional Cookies</h3>
    <p class="mt-2">
      <strong>Purpose:</strong> These cookies are necessary for the website to function properly.
    </p>
    <table class="mt-3 w-full border-collapse text-xs">
      <thead>
        <tr class="border-b border-border">
          <th class="border-r border-border px-3 py-2 text-left">Cookie Name</th>
          <th class="border-r border-border px-3 py-2 text-left">Purpose</th>
          <th class="px-3 py-2 text-left">Duration</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr class="border-b border-border">
          <td class="border-r border-border px-3 py-2">json-formatter-pro</td>
          <td class="border-r border-border px-3 py-2">Stores user preferences (theme, indentation) and last input</td>
          <td class="px-3 py-2">Until cleared</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h3 class="mt-6 text-base font-semibold text-fg">2. Analytics Cookies</h3>
    <p class="mt-2">
      <strong>Purpose:</strong> Help us understand how visitors use the website and improve performance.
    </p>
    <table class="mt-3 w-full border-collapse text-xs">
      <thead>
        <tr class="border-b border-border">
          <th class="border-r border-border px-3 py-2 text-left">Provider</th>
          <th class="border-r border-border px-3 py-2 text-left">Purpose</th>
          <th class="px-3 py-2 text-left">Duration</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr class="border-b border-border">
          <td class="border-r border-border px-3 py-2">Cloudflare Web Analytics</td>
          <td class="border-r border-border px-3 py-2">Aggregate page view counts (cookieless)</td>
          <td class="px-3 py-2">Not applicable</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h3 class="mt-6 text-base font-semibold text-fg">3. Advertising Cookies</h3>
    <p class="mt-2">
      <strong>Purpose:</strong> Display relevant advertisements and measure advertising effectiveness.
    </p>
    <table class="mt-3 w-full border-collapse text-xs">
      <thead>
        <tr class="border-b border-border">
          <th class="border-r border-border px-3 py-2 text-left">Provider</th>
          <th class="border-r border-border px-3 py-2 text-left">Purpose</th>
          <th class="px-3 py-2 text-left">Duration</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr class="border-b border-border">
          <td class="border-r border-border px-3 py-2">Google AdSense</td>
          <td class="border-r border-border px-3 py-2">Serve personalized ads, measure campaign performance</td>
          <td class="px-3 py-2">13 months</td>
        </tr>
        <tr class="border-b border-border">
          <td class="border-r border-border px-3 py-2">Google Analytics</td>
          <td class="border-r border-border px-3 py-2">Track user behavior for advertising insights</td>
          <td class="px-3 py-2">13 months</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h2 class="mt-8 text-lg font-semibold text-fg">How We Use Cookie Information</h2>
    <ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6">
      <li><strong>Functionality:</strong> Remember your preferences and settings</li>
      <li><strong>Analytics:</strong> Understand visitor behavior and improve the website</li>
      <li><strong>Advertising:</strong> Display relevant ads and measure their performance</li>
      <li><strong>Security:</strong> Detect and prevent fraud and abuse</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="mt-8 text-lg font-semibold text-fg">Your Cookie Choices</h2>

    <h3 class="mt-6 text-base font-semibold text-fg">Browser Settings</h3>
    <p class="mt-2">
      Most browsers allow you to refuse cookies or alert you when cookies are being sent. You can typically find cookie controls in your browser's settings under "Privacy" or "Security". Here are links to manage cookies in popular browsers:
    </p>
    <ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-6">
      <li><a href="https://support.google.com/chrome/answer/95647" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary hover:underline">Google Chrome</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://support.mozilla.org/en-US/kb/enhanced-tracking-protection-firefox-desktop" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary hover:underline">Mozilla Firefox</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://support.apple.com/en-us/HT201265" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary hover:underline">Apple Safari</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/help/4468242/microsoft-edge-browsing-data-and-privacy-microsoft-privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary hover:underline">Microsoft Edge</a></li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="mt-6 text-base font-semibold text-fg">Opt-Out of Advertising Cookies</h3>
    <p class="mt-2">
      You can opt out of personalized advertising by:
    </p>
    <ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-6">
      <li>Visiting <a href="https://adssettings.google.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary hover:underline">Google Ads Settings</a></li>
      <li>Enabling "Do Not Track" in your browser</li>
      <li>Using an ad blocker or privacy extension</li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="mt-6 text-base font-semibold text-fg">Clear Cookies</h3>
    <p class="mt-2">
      You can clear cookies stored by JSON Formatter Pro:
    </p>
    <ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-6">
      <li>Manually clear your browser cache and cookies</li>
      <li>Use your browser's "Clear Browsing Data" or "Clear Cache" function</li>
      <li>Note: Clearing cookies will reset your preferences and last input</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="mt-8 text-lg font-semibold text-fg">Third-Party Cookies</h2>
    <p class="mt-2">
      Google AdSense and Google Analytics set cookies on your device when you visit JSON Formatter Pro. These are "third-party" cookies because they are set by domains other than json-formatter-pro.com.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-3">
      <strong>Third-party cookie providers:</strong>
    </p>
    <ul class="mt-2 list-disc space-y-1 pl-6">
      <li><strong>Google:</strong> <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary hover:underline">Privacy Policy</a> and <a href="https://policies.google.com/terms" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary hover:underline">Terms</a></li>
      <li><strong>Cloudflare:</strong> <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary hover:underline">Privacy Policy</a></li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="mt-8 text-lg font-semibold text-fg">Do Not Track (DNT)</h2>
    <p class="mt-2">
      Some browsers include a "Do Not Track" (DNT) feature. JSON Formatter Pro currently does not respond to DNT signals, but respecting your privacy remains important to us. We recommend using your browser's privacy settings for cookie control.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-8 text-lg font-semibold text-fg">Policy Updates</h2>
    <p class="mt-2">
      We may update this Cookie Policy from time to time. Changes will be effective immediately upon posting to this page. Your continued use of JSON Formatter Pro following the posting of revised Cookie Policy means you accept and agree to the changes.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-8 text-lg font-semibold text-fg">Questions?</h2>
    <p class="mt-2">
      If you have questions about our use of cookies, please <a href="/contact" class="text-primary hover:underline">contact us</a> or email hashcode.dev@gmail.com.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
